item.description:
Don't forget to enter the Friends of Myles Standish State Forest 2nd Annual Photo Contest! The deadline is September 1. Many of you have already posted great pictures on this site. Select your best 3 and send them to friends@friendsmssf.com. You'll find an entry form in the "Files" section. The photos must have been taken between Sept. 15, 2009 and Sept. 1, 2010. Anyone can enter, even the President of FMSSF. But don't worry. We hold a blind judging using real artists. You can see all of the 2009 entries and the winners at www.friendsmssf.com. Good luck!
